sequenceDiagram
  actor User
  participant Web as Web App
  participant Server as Server Layer
  participant DB as Database
  participant Data as Data Layer
  participant Score as Scoring
  participant Report as Report Service

  User->>Web: select area or object
  User->>Web: choose scenario or custom query
  Web->>Server: submit analysis request
  Server->>DB: validate project and context
  Server->>DB: create analysis record
  Server->>Data: request source context
  Data-->>Server: return context package
  Server->>Score: calculate scores
  Score-->>Server: return score package
  Server->>DB: save analysis result
  Server-->>Web: return dashboard data
  Web-->>User: render dashboard
  User->>Web: request report export
  Web->>Server: submit report request
  Server->>Report: generate report
  Report->>DB: save report metadata
  Server-->>Web: return report status

